== Further Reading

#parec[
  Donald Knuth's article _Literate Programming_ (@Knuth1984) describes the main ideas behind literate programming as well as his web programming environment. The seminal TEX typesetting system was written with web and has been published as a series of books (@Knuth1986; @Knuth1993a). Knuth and Levy presented the implementation of the cweb literate programming system as a literate program (@Knuth1994). Knuth has also published both a collection of graph algorithms in The Stanford GraphBase (@Knuth1993b) and a simulator for the _MMIX_ instruction set (@Knuth1999) in literate format. These programs are enjoyable to read and are excellent presentations of their respective algorithms. The website #link("http://www.literateprogramming.com/")[www.literateprogramming.com] has pointers to many articles about literate programming, literate programs to download, and a variety of literate programming systems; many refinements have been made since Knuth's original development of the idea.
][
  唐纳德·克努斯（Donald Knuth）在他的文章《文学编程》(@Knuth1984) 中描述了文学编程背后的主要思想以及他的 web 编程环境。开创性的 TEX 排版系统就是用 web 编写并以一系列书籍的形式出版的 (@Knuth1986; @Knuth1993a)。克努斯和 Levy 展示了 cweb 文学编程系统的实现，也是以文学程序的形式呈现的 (@Knuth1994)。克努斯还以文学格式出版了一系列图算法的集合《斯坦福图基础》(@Knuth1993b)以及 _MMIX_ 指令集的模拟器 (@Knuth1999)。这些程序阅读起来令人愉快，是各自算法的优秀展示。网站 #link("http://www.literateprogramming.com/")[www.literateprogramming.com] 提供了关于文学编程的许多文章的链接、可下载的文学程序和各种文学编程系统；自克努斯最初发展这一理念以来，已有许多改进。
]

#parec[
  Other literate programs we know of that have been published as books include one on the implementation of the lcc compiler, which was written by Christopher Fraser and David Hanson and published as A Retargetable C Compiler: Design and Implementation @Fraser95. See also Hanson's book on program interface design (@Hanson96), Mehlhorn and Näher's presentation on the implementation of the LEDA library (@Mehlhorn99), Valiente's collection of graph algorithms (@Valiente02), and Ruckert's description of the mp3 audio format (@Ruckert05).
][
  我们所知道的其他以书籍形式出版的文学程序还包括一个关于 lcc 编译器实现的程序，该程序由克里斯托弗·弗雷泽（Christopher Fraser）和大卫·汉森（David Hanson）编写，并出版为《可重定目标的 C 编译器：设计与实现》@Fraser95。另见汉森关于程序接口设计的书籍 (@Hanson96)，梅尔霍恩（Mehlhorn）和奈尔（Näher）关于 LEDA 库实现的介绍 (@Mehlhorn99)，瓦连特（Valiente）的图算法集合 (@Valiente02)，以及鲁克特（Ruckert）对 mp3 音频格式的描述 (@Ruckert05)。
]
